With the class GpioManager you can control the output board LS-373 (support for inputs not yet implemented)
Scheme and the location of the pins you can find in the manual of mainboard on page 29

Table of outputs:
Logical PIN  |  Mainobard PIN
0                        3
1                        5
2                        7
3                        9
4                        4
5                        6
6                        8
7                        10

Digital output closes the circuit to ground.

